{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Night_Out_On_Coruscant",
  "title": "A Night Out on Coruscant",
  "summary": "In a Coruscant hospital, the Jedi-in-training and physician Brandis -- recovering from the loss of a hand on Selene and awaiting a cybernetic graft -- is unexpectedly reunited with Colonel Sabrina Rheatis, there for a routine physical before her transfer to Mon Calamari. She comforts him through his grief and guilt, and after his successful surgery he finally persuades her to join him for dinner. Over crab legs at a hole-in-the-wall restaurant they trade secrets and grow close, sharing a kiss that turns the evening intimate. Knowing Sabrina ships out at dawn, Brandis offers to help her pack and accompanies her back to the officers' barracks, where she asks him not to leave; the two spend the night together, and the log closes the next morning with the pair reluctant to part as her departure for Calamari looms.",
